##### 880-125 Covered sovereign entities



A *sovereign entity is covered by this section if it satisfies all of the

following requirements:



(a) the entity is funded solely by public monies;



(b) all returns on the entity’s investments are public monies;



(c) the entity is not a partnership;



(d) the entity is not any of the following:



(i) a *public non-financial entity;



(ii) a *public financial entity (other than a public financial

entity that only carries on central banking activities).
